Exercise 1: SLF4J – Logging Error Messages and Warning Levels
Using SLF4J with org.slf4j.simple backend to log errors and warnings.

Description:
This code logs:
✅ INFO on successful login
⚠ WARN on incorrect login
❌ ERROR if username or password is null
It uses SLF4J with a simple backend (you must include JARs below).

Expected Output:
INFO  LoginService - User authenticated successfully
WARN  LoginService - Failed login attempt for user: admin
ERROR LoginService - Username or password is null
